HEADWORD: Redbud
<hw>Red"bud`</hw> <pr>(-b?d`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A small ornamental leguminous tree of the American species of the
genus <gen>Cercis</gen>. See <cref>Judas tree</cref>, under
<er>Judas</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

